    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is accepted given the prescriptive single-condition protocol mandated by ASTM F1717 and the otherwise high overall credibility evidence. Overall model credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission.",
